-- UBM Buys Majority Stake in Brazilian Presentation Company Sienna Interlink
-- Tim Farrand
-- 2010-06-14T06:05:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/ubm-buys-majority-stake-in-brazilian-presentation-company-sienna-interlink.html

          
          
             United Business Media said it
acquired a 75 percent stake in Sienna Interlink, a Brazilian
exhibition company based in Sao Paulo.  
          
          


  


        